{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5c39aebc55","title":"陶铸与河北大学马曙光等的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"323f65dbb2","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":20,"articleId":"5c39aebc55"}],"tags":[{"id":"258ff30391","name":"河北文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dbcf15bd08","name":"陶铸","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fc9bf1b7c1","type":"title","text":"陶铸与河北大学马曙光等的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5c39aebc55"},{"id":"5fb8937320","type":"paragraph","text":"张庆奎：我们是河北大学的（陶铸同志一一和我们握手）","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5c39aebc55"},{"id":"30c4633724","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸：你们来多少人？","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5c39aebc55"},{"id":"dea2ba1ed2","type":"paragraph","text":"马曙光：四百多人（把材料交给陶铸同志）","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5c39aebc55"},{"id":"9f2742c796","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸：你们住在哪里？","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5c39aebc55"},{"id":"be78a0a02a","type":"paragraph","text":"马曙光等：外交学院。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5c39aebc55"},{"id":"680113983a","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸：你们回去，回去继续搞革命。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5c39aebc55"},{"id":"1d0ec7b39a","type":"paragraph","text":"马曙光：这不光是我们学校的问题，是河北省委和我们的问题，我们有人提出“炮轰省委司令部”，省委的同志讲炮轰省委司令员就是反省委、反党！","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5c39aebc55"},{"id":"be5f596b0e","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸：省委问题也要轰，你们可以和他们辩论。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5c39aebc55"},{"id":"b5c878d676","type":"paragraph","text":"马曙光：我们要和他辩论，他们不辩，他们发动天津市的工人、学生、机关干部向我们围攻，声讨我们。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5c39aebc55"},{"id":"23ab9fae5d","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸：你们革他们的命就要有阻力，他们这种作法就是反革命。不革命就是反革命！你们要顶住，不要怕。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5c39aebc55"},{"id":"ce25d6eef5","type":"paragraph","text":"马曙光等：我们不怕。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5c39aebc55"},{"id":"d8587199d7","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸：我们把你们的材料交给文革小组。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5c39aebc55"}],"page":{"id":"ce74ef691c","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5c39aebc55","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}